reviewText: if you know what you came here for you won't be disappointed. just get it and relive the glory of the 85 chicago bears' goofy super bowl rap song. if you are wondering why they are such slow, stiff dancers its because this video was made after they lost their ONLY defeat of the season the night before to the miami dolphins on MNF. the song was filmed first thing in the morning. it didn't put a dent in their swagger, only their dance moves.
